comments:
Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parishes of Huyton 
    with Roby, Kirkby and Prescot. See also Table 2, notes (b) (f), (g), (h), (i), 
    (j) and (k).

Created 1.4.1983 out of the Knowsley unparished area and the parish 
    of Whiston. See also Table 2, notes (h) and (i).

Abolished 1.1.2015 and added to the Knowsley unparished area. 
    See also Table 2, notes (b), (d) and (e).
